She has her own nonprofit, coderGirls (www.codergirls.org), and is a second degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do. She is also a NCWIT National Award Winner and a Stanford #include fellow. Her favorite thing about being a girl who codes is how creative coding is and how she is able apply problem solving.
